ww.nytimes.com/2025/01/23/books/dalai-lama-book-voice-for-the-voiceless.html</link><description>这位西藏的精神领袖出版了大量有关政治的著作，但很少有深入的著作。如今，年近 90 岁的他分享了自己数十年来与中国打交道的详细个人经历。</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Jan 2025 20:00:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2025/01/23/books/dalai-lama-book-voice-for-the-voiceless.html</guid></item><item><title>书评：《一切都必须过去》，作者：Dorian Lynskey</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2025/01/22/books/review/everything-must-go-dorian-lynskey.html</link><description>英国文化记者多里安·林斯基（Dorian Lynskey）的一本新书记录了我们几个世纪以来对世界末日场景的痴迷。</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 10:01:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2025/01/22/books/review/everything-must-go-dorian-lynskey.html</guid></item><item><title>尖刻漫画家、作家及其他人士 Jules Feiffer 去世，享年 95 岁</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2025/01/21/arts/jules-feiffer-dead.html</link><description>在他长篇连载的《乡村之声》漫画以及他的许多戏剧和剧本中，他热衷于讽刺政治、人际关系和人性。</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 01:56:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2025/01/21/arts/jules-feiffer-dead.html</guid></item><item><title>2025 年最受期待的书籍改编作品：电影和电视节目</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/article/book-movie-tv-adaptations-2025.html</link><description>希拉里·曼特尔的《镜子与光》、新版《布里奇特·琼斯》和迈克尔·邦德的《帕丁顿熊》系列都是今年最受期待的改编作品。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 16:46:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/article/book-movie-tv-adaptations-2025.html</guid></item><item><title>你能找到多少本故事中隐藏的书名？</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/interactive/2025/01/21/books/review/midcentury-books-search.html</link><description>这个简短的场景隐藏了 20 世纪中叶出版的 13 本书的名称。看看你是否能找到所有这些内容并在此过程中建立一个阅读清单。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 13:30:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/interactive/2025/01/21/books/review/midcentury-books-search.html</guid></item></channel></rss>